  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dc3 13  \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5 \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca 15 \u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5 \u0da2\u0dba \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sanahas, who won the age 13 level, will win the 15 level",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 15-year-old child has appeared in the last General Certificate of Studies A-level examination and obtained three B grades.",
        "This child, Dewum Sanahas Ranasinghe, who is currently studying in the 9th grade of an international school in Kadavata area, passed his G.E.C. in the 8th grade. (Ordinary Text) Examination and obtained A-6 passes, B-2 passes and C-1 passes.",
        "Sanahas, who has managed to score 173 marks in the five-year scholarship, appeared in the General Examination at the age of 13.",
        "He said that Sanahas, who has a passion for cricket, is looking forward to the field of law.",
        "Sanahas is the eldest in a family of three children, his mother and father work as teachers in the school where he studies.",
        "Mrs. Malka Ranasinghe, the mother, stated that they are discussing to admit Sanahas to a public university or a private university."
      ],
